title: Resort Style Living Sigle Family Home for Rent
posting_body: ["You'll find space and style in this lake-view home located in the resort-style Olympia community.", "Here you'll find an open-concept floor plan featuring updated fixtures and finishes and design details including tile flooring, arched windows, updated lighting.", 'Lovely kitchen includes stainless steel appliances, custom cabinetry, and an expansive seated bar for casual dining.', "Owner's suite features ample closet space and en suite bath with double-sink and seated vanities.", 'Your favorite spot might just be the elegant, private lanai, offering a screened terrace with plenty of room for outdoor seating, dining and entertaining.', 'Enjoy the convenience of double-bay garage; panel shutters offer added storm protection and peace of mind.', 'Rent includes high speed ATT internet, 4 manned gates, and onsite security at all times of the day!', 'TOP Rated Schools!!!', 'Close to Mall, super market and major highways!', 'Everything about this community screams luxury!', 'To start off the community is an Award winning community with resort amenities that include a gigantic pool with private cabanas and splash park for kids!', 'The club house offers outdoor and indoor basketball courts, pickle ball court, tennis court, volleyball court, decked out clubhouse, and an impressive fitness center!', ' Not to mention a brand new play ground for the kiddos!', 'This community has something for everyone of all ages!', 'Move in requirements:', 'Clean background', '680+ Credit Score', 'First, Last, Security', 'And Association Deposit.', 'Contact Nicole Berdecia Massanet with EXP Realty for more info', 'show contact info']
